  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为混合线程（Hilos Mixtos）的安全架构做一份甘特图，第一部分聚焦在零信任安全模型（Security ZeroTrust）上。整体时间轴用毫秒级精度，从0到16毫秒。你能先帮我搭个框架吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "hilos",
        "mixtos",
        "security zerotrust",
        "axisFormat %sms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，毫秒级时间轴。我看到标题里提到了Security_Firewall和Security_OAuth2，这两个是并行的安全层吗？还有P1、P2、P3这三个部分，我需要确认它们的从属关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "security firewall",
        "security oauth2",
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P1对应Security_OAuth2认证层，P2和P3都是Security_Firewall防火墙层。P1只有一个线程T1，P2有T1和T2两个线程，P3有T1、T2、T3三个线程。我们先画P1的部分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "t1",
        "t2",
        "t3",
        "security oauth2",
        "security firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，P1的T1_exec从0毫秒开始执行，持续4毫秒，标记为active状态。然后T1_IO在6毫秒开始，做3毫秒的临界I/O操作。这两个任务之间留了2毫秒的空档，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1-t1_exec",
        "p1-t1_io",
        "active",
        "crit",
        "0",
        "4",
        "6",
        "9"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，那个空档是留给调度开销的。现在画P2，T1_exec从4毫秒开始执行4毫秒，然后T2_exec在12毫秒开始执行2毫秒，T2_IO紧接着做2毫秒的临界操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2-t1_exec",
        "p2-t2_exec",
        "p2-t2_io",
        "4",
        "8",
        "12",
        "14",
        "16"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P2部分已添加。P3的T1_exec我放在8到12毫秒，和P2的T1_exec有重叠，这是故意的并行设计吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3-t1_exec",
        "8",
        "12",
        "p2-t1_exec"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，P2-T1和P3-T1是并行执行的。另外P3-T2有个ULT（用户级线程）操作，也是8到12毫秒，但状态要标为done，表示这是预完成的初始化工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3-t2_ult",
